These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, d&b, electronic
1. the fan of d&b is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is between the fan of electronic and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | coffee | mirinda | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | blues    | electronic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, scientist, paramedic
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the paramedic is between the nurse and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | hiking    | writing        | gardening |
| Job     | scientist | paramedic | nurse         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, soy-milk
3 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the owner of the goat and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | lemonade | coffee     | soy-milk |
| Pet        | goat  | hedgehog | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, classical
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, snake
1. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the fan of classical is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | classical     | dubstep |
| Pet           | cat | snake | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, puzzles, drawing
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, goldfish
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | drawing     | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | goldfish    | lizard | rabbit    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, polish, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is badminton is between the japanese and the argentine##2
2. the argentine is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the polish is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | argentine  | polish   | japanese        |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, papaya, cranberry
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, thai, egyptian
1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the indonesian is between the person eating cranberry and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | papaya  | pepper  | cranberry |
| Nationality   | thai | indonesian | egyptian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, documentary, superhero
There are 3 different nationalities: german, dutch, american
1. the person watching documentary movies is the american##1
2. the dutch is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | family  | documentary  |
| Nationality   | german | dutch | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, bike, trike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | surfing | snowboarding | cycling  |
| Transport   | trike    | scooter        | bike |

 #################################

 
