.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, cola
There 3 different types of food: avocado, artichoke, cherry
1. the person eating cherry is between the person drinking tea and the person eating avocado##2
2. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate      | cola      |
| Food       | artichoke  | cherry | avocado |

