2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | house | jazz   | trance   |
| Sport         | cycling | ice-hockey | skateboarding |

