.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, blues, house
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking fanta and the fan of blues##2
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta | almond-milk   | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | house  | rock | blues   |

 